two types of fuctions are available to update a document
    - db.collections.updateOne({ <filter> }, { <values to update> })
    - db.collections.updateMany({ <filter> }, { <values to update> })

$set - is used to set value to a filed 

    syntax - db.collections.updateOne({name: "Tharun"}, {$set: {age: 22}})

$unset - is used to exclude value from a filed 

    syntax - db.collections.updateOne({name: "Tharun"}, {$unset: {age: ""}})

    